480</Width><Height>308</Height><Bytes>33609</Bytes><Caption>2631759-PortAventura-Hotel-Property-Amenity-4</Caption><ThumbnailUrl>/RXLImages/1116/78/15/91/2631759-PortAventura-Hotel-Property-Amenity-4thumb.jpg</ThumbnailUrl><ThumbnailWidth>109</ThumbnailWidth><ThumbnailHeight>70</ThumbnailHeight><ThumbnailBytes>2847</ThumbnailBytes><PhotoType>ExternalViewOfTheHotel</PhotoType></Photo><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>General</Type><Text>With direct access to the Mediterranea area of PortAventura Park, this Mediterranean-style hotel is a replica of a quaint fishing village, with splendid sweeping gardens and magnificent lake.
De-stress after a hectic day at PortAventura Park and forget everything in this charming hamlet,  very close to the sea, with its little villas surrounded by exuberant plant-life and two fantastic outdoor swimming pools. 
At Hotel PortAventura you will find all the necessary ingredients for a few days of relaxation, peace and, at the same time, escape and fun. Free Wi-Fi is available throughout the hotel and there is a wide range of typical authentic Mediterranean cuisine.
In this hotel you feel the vitality, quality of life and healthy customs for which the towns of the Mediterranean are so famous.  
An authentic Costa Dorada villa where you are able to keep in shape at the gym, use the saunas, steam baths and jacuzzi and enjoy a pleasurable massage, your biggest allies after an intrepid day out at PortAventura Park.  
Access to PortAventura Park is unlimited and admission is included in the price of your stay.

Please note that for stays for December 24th and 31st, 2012, there is a mandatory gala dinner included in the price).</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>SurroundingArea</Type><Text>Salou is a mere 10-15 minute journey away depending on your means of travel and offers a lively resort all year round, with plenty of bars, restaurants and shops. Travel North by train from PortAventura's own railway station and you are welcomed by the enchanting city of Barcelona.
Located at the entrance to PortAventura Park and PortAventura Aquatic Park, 5 minutes from Salou center by car and 1 hour to Barcelona.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>RoomTypes</Type><Text>STANDARD - 4_STAR - Entrance to PortAventura Park included (Check the opening schedule PortAventura Park).
